casebody.data:
URIARTE
v.
SCOTT SALES COMPANY S220088 Supreme Court of California December 14, 2016

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Review in the above-captioned matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Second Appellate District, Division One with directions to vacate its decision and to reconsider the case in light of Ramos v. Brenntag Specialties, Inc. (2016) 63 Cal.4th 500, 203 Cal.Rptr.3d 273, 372 P.3d 200. (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
